| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3363 — Recovery Inhibition (kairos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a9eff323-fdc2-5b46-a8ca-8b0c0c1c6b86"
